rlm-gh-browse

Open the current GitHub repository in the browser at the branch
currently checked out. Resolves the branch with
`git branch --show-current` and hands it to `gh repo view -w -b
<branch>`, which opens the repo's web page for that branch. Refuses
when not inside a git repository or when HEAD is detached (no current
branch to open).

REQUIRES
  gh, git
